\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Based on the above discussion, the proposed closed form optimum frame length
 
\begin_inset Formula $L_{MCRC}$
\end_inset

 under the multiple collision recovery coefficients environment is:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\size scriptsize
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
L_{MCRC}=\left(-\frac{b}{4a}+S+0.5\sqrt{-4S^{2}-2P-\frac{q}{S}}\right)\cdot n\label{eq:closed form}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\size default
According to (
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:closed form"

\end_inset

), the proposed equation gives a linear relation wrt.
 the number of tags 
\begin_inset Formula $n$
\end_inset

, and includes the effect of different collision recovery coefficients.
